title: [Tolwynn's Outfitting]
[Tolwynn's General Store]
description: Beneath an ebonwood beam ceiling, a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin hangs on one of the varnished ebonwood walls.  A jewel-inlaid caddy and a glass-topped mistwood counter sit in opposite corners while a stuffed striped rolton rests on a glossy mahogany floor.
